3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the performance analysis of a communication system, which can be viewed as a control system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses physical layer network coding, which is a technique commonly used in multimedia communication systems. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper does not directly deal with cryptography or security, but the concepts discussed in the paper can be applied to secure communication systems.
